{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"14805-beloved-daughter","title":"Beloved Daughter","description":"Natabo has run away from her home! Do you know why?","language":"English","langCode":"en","isRtl":false,"level":"1","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Mulongo  Bukheye ","Ritah  Katetemera "],"illustrators":["Brian Wambi"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"African Storybook Initiative","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/14805-beloved-daughter"},"cover":{"card":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/40624/size3/b747473e2f2e9cb6a0c0052c4aaf3564.jpg","large":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/40624/size6/b747473e2f2e9cb6a0c0052c4aaf3564.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/40625/size6/51b59ee1ed292554550725249ee139bc.jpg","text":"This is Natabo.\nShe has six brothers.","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/40626/size6/75cbd7ff5d27ba81270a3752cc5ce6c3.jpg","text":"Her parents give\nher a small pot. She loves it.","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/40627/size6/488b6b4a00ec2b9fcd9872a98d8e9467.jpg","text":"One day her\nbrothers break the pot.","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/40629/size6/0eecf2a4b138e96119bbaaad623c1243.jpg","text":"Natabo cannot\nfind her pot. She cries and cries.","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/40630/size6/77a1604b52e79d0e8ff00037025fa1e2.jpg","text":"Natabo runs away.\nShe climbs a tall tree.","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/40631/size6/e47683b6c510ac24c06d09b73cdbf935.jpg","text":"Her parents find\nher. \"Please\ncome\ndown,\" they\nask.","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/40632/size6/dcf01572f2e85361d8a0acae905816ca.jpg","text":"Her brothers\nsing, \"Please come down.\"","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/40633/size6/a667e7fd4322e2756e055fa2e8b2fddf.jpg","text":"Natabo makes fun of their song.","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/40634/size6/8f9c39f61f952db617e26b1567d7b302.jpg","text":"Then Natabo's friend comes. \"Please come down,\" she sings.","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/40635/size6/c30ce0ff590aa676f148f5053902bcbe.jpg","text":"Natabo's friend sings until she comes down from the tree.","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/40638/size6/e20a550e357a442f4cb6c39e433e128b.jpg","text":"The friends walk\nhome together.","words":null},{"n":12,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/40640/size6/96359a3c38cabd9460e2bcc31617af25.jpg","text":"Everyone celebrates that Natabo is home. Natabo gets a new pot!","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":12,"words":97}}